We're thrilled to launch our new navigation, making it easier to find jobs through our streamlined search and filter options.
You can see the status of your last application, view job recommendations, read reviews from the best organisation(s) and update your profile with the simple format, to boost your chances of being noticed by an advertiser.
As ever, if you find or experience any issues with the app, please let us know at usersupport@seek.com.au

Be notified when an employer has viewed your application by turning on your push notifications.
We've also added the ability for you to hide your "approachability" from potential employers. We calculate whether you are "approachable" based on your activity on SEEK, to indicate to employers you may be interested in new opportunities.

Be notified when an employer has viewed your application by turning on your push notifications.
We've also added the ability for you to hide your "approachability" from potential employers. We calculate whether you are "approachable" based on your activity on SEEK, to indicate to employers you may be interested in new opportunities.

The weather’s heating up down under and so are our releases:
* Introducing ‘Company Search’ - search for roles at the the employer whose aircon is going to keep you feeling cool
* Bug squashing - the creepy crawlies couldn’t handle our heat, so they’re gone

As always, feedback is very welcome. Simply email us at usersupport@seek.com.au

Hi jobseekers, whatever holiday you celebrate this time of year, we have a gift for you:
- We’re making it easier for you to stand out on the app by adding detailed education and a Summary field to SEEK Profile.
- We also have a gorgeous new design for SEEK Profile with slicker navigation.

From all of us at SEEK, we hope you have a great holiday season!

Hey there, we've been working on some pretty cool things that we think you'll love…

• We've made your job search even easier with auto-suggest job titles when you're searching for jobs
• We've simplified how to add career information to your Seek profile on the go so that you can standout to hirers
• There were some pesky bugs that were trying to make your experience worse, we neutralised them

Just another way we're helping you find that dream job.
As ever, if you find or experience any issues with the app, please let us know at usersupport@seek.com.au
